
-------------- Indexing and slicing :--------------------------

1) Indexing: 
   Accesses individual elements of an array using zero-based indices.

2) Slicing: 
   Extracts subsets or ranges of elements from an array.

3) Advanced Indexing: 
   Uses integer arrays or boolean masks for more complex data extraction.  

   fancy Indexing : selecting multiple indexing at once 
   